      "name": "FDA pump PIV velocity field comparison — 5 operating points",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations compared against CFD velocity predictions. Mean relative error 8.3%; peak shear stress prediction within 12% of experimental values. Provides primary quantitative basis for model form credibility claim."
    },
    {
