      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterisation of biological variability in test blood samples; donor-to-donor variability in red-cell fragility documented and propagated.",
      "rationale": "Bench experiments used pooled bovine blood from a single lot. Donor-to-donor variability in red-cell fragility was not characterised. At MRL 5 this factor requires full statistical sample characterisation. Flagged as epistemic gap; not-assessed."
    },
